answerText: Hulu[10] In the U.S., Hulu is home to this show starring Xander Berkeley. The plot revolves The Man, who resides at the title location and gives people tasks from a mysterious book that if completed, will grant that task doer their wish.

question: Question: In January 2013, Jason Kilar, the CEO of this joint venture of NBC, Fox, and Disney resigned.
